### Community Launch Playbook
```markdown
# Launching a Brand Community

## Phase 1: Foundation (Weeks -8 to -4)

### Define the Community
- [ ] Purpose statement documented
- [ ] Target member profile created
- [ ] Value proposition articulated
- [ ] Community guidelines drafted
- [ ] Success metrics defined

### Choose Platform
| Platform | Best For | Pros | Cons |
|----------|----------|------|------|
| Slack | Professional/B2B | Familiar, threaded | Limited features |
| Discord | Engaged/younger | Feature-rich, free | Learning curve |
| Circle | Community-first | Purpose-built | Monthly cost |
| Mighty Networks | Courses + community | All-in-one | Can feel heavy |
| Facebook Groups | Broad reach | Easy to join | Algorithm issues |

### Platform Setup
- [ ] Community space created
- [ ] Channels/categories structured
- [ ] Welcome flow designed
- [ ] Bot/automation configured
- [ ] Guidelines posted
- [ ] FAQ ready

## Phase 2: Seed Members (Weeks -4 to 0)

### Founding Member Strategy
**Goal:** 50-100 founding members before public launch

**Who to Invite First:**
1. Existing customers (most engaged)
2. Power users and superfans
3. Industry connections
4. Team members and investors
5. Friends of the brand

**Founding Member Benefits:**
- Early access forever
- Special badge/role
- Input on community direction
- Exclusive founding member channel
- First access to new features

**Outreach Template:**
```
Subject: You're invited to join [Community Name] as a founding member

Hey [Name],

We're building something special - [Community Name], a community for [persona] to [value prop].

Given your [reason they're special], we'd love to have you as one of our founding members.

As a founder, you'll get:
- [Benefit 1]
- [Benefit 2]
- [Benefit 3]

Interested? [Join link]

[Your name]
```

### Pre-Launch Engagement
- [ ] Welcome all founding members personally
- [ ] Seed initial discussions
- [ ] Host founding member kickoff call
- [ ] Gather feedback on structure
- [ ] Build initial content bank

## Phase 3: Public Launch (Week 0)

### Launch Day Activities
- [ ] Announcement across all channels
- [ ] Founding members invited to share
- [ ] Welcome thread for new members
- [ ] Live kickoff event (AMA, intro call)
- [ ] Active engagement from team

### Launch Week Content
```
Day 1: Welcome + introduce yourself thread
Day 2: First AMA or discussion topic
Day 3: Resource sharing thread
Day 4: Wins/celebrations thread
Day 5: Community member spotlight
Day 6: Weekend casual thread
Day 7: Weekly roundup + what's coming
```

## Phase 4: Sustain & Grow (Ongoing)

### Weekly Rhythm
| Day | Activity |
|-----|----------|
| Monday | Weekly kickoff post, goals thread |
| Tuesday | Learning/resource sharing |
| Wednesday | AMA or expert session |
| Thursday | Discussion/debate topic |
| Friday | Wins celebration, shoutouts |

### Monthly Rituals
- [ ] Member spotlight feature
- [ ] Community metrics review
- [ ] Content calendar planning
- [ ] Member feedback survey
- [ ] Virtual or IRL event
```

